428
00:18:53,633 --> 00:18:57,469
Toma esa. Gracias. 24…

429
00:18:57,470 --> 00:19:00,439
Tres, dos, uno…

430
00:19:00,440 --> 00:19:06,045
¡Adelante!

431
00:19:06,046 --> 00:19:11,016
